HEADWORD: Overbrow
<hw>O`ver*brow"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To hang over
like a brow; to impend over.</def> <mark>[Poetic]</mark>
<rj><au>Longfellow.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Did with a huge projection <qex>overbrow</qex>⟦br⟧
